                            <comment id="12550668" author="stack" created="Tue, 11 Dec 2007 18:30:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Do you mean the clone issue?  If so, no.  Folks like this tool (see comments on the list).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
